subsection.p:
Add all six faces:
\iint_{\partial B}\mathbf F\cdot\widehat{\mathbf n}\,dS \amp= hk\ell+2hk\ell+3hk\ell \amp= 6hk\ell.
The volume of the box is hk\ell. So \boxed{ \iint_{\partial B}\mathbf F\cdot\widehat{\mathbf n}\,dS = 6\,\operatorname{Volume}(B). }

